snippet.title: BOC: Birth of Cultures | On Steam OST Preview
snippet.description: BoC is a historical strategy game: Actual planets, climate simulation, and a non-linear progression over the last 60,000 years of human evolution. Develop your own ancient civilization starting as a nomad tribe from the last Ice Age.
